text: Justice Elio Smith (born August 9, 1995) is an American actor. He is best known for playing Radar in the movie Paper Towns (2015), Ezekiel in the Netflix television series The Get Down (2016–2017) and as Franklin in Jurassic World: Fallen Kingdom. Smith will star in Pokémon: Detective Pikachu (2019). He was born in Los Angeles, California.
